# Prompt

## Left Prompt

### List of information

  [Always on]
  Current user name
    Red if root
    Orange if su ?
  Current machine
  Current folder
    Red: can't write on current folder

  [Context dependant]
  Error code
    If error on previous command
  Connection status
    Internet access
    Wireless / USB / Wired access
    IPv6 (displayed) / IPv4 (hidden)



## Right Prompt

## Status line
  This is the line a the bottom of the terminal
  Hide for small windows

  [Always on]
  Current mode
    vi / emacs
  Time and date

  [Context dependant]
  Battery status
    If laptop
    If remote laptop (no access to display server)
  Current vi mode (normal / insert / visual)
    If in vi mode
  CPU / Disk usage
  Version Control (git)
    If in a repo
